OL,3,CStormzy fined for using phone while
OL,4,Cdriving #400,000 Ferrari
OL,6,FStormzy has been fined more than #500
OL,7,Fafter he was caught by police while
OL,8,Fusing a mobile phone at the wheel of
OL,9,Fhis #400,000 Ferrari.
OL,11,FThe rapper, 32, was pulled over by a
OL,12,FMetropolitan Police constable after
OL,13,Fbeing spotted typing an address into
OL,14,Fhis phone's map application while in
OL,15,Fstationary traffic.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
