CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780585869
OL,3,CStormzy fined for using phone while
OL,4,Cdriving #400,000 Ferrari
OL,6,FHe admitted the offence at the
OL,7,Froadside last November near his home
OL,8,Fin Kingston upon Thames, south-west
OL,9,FLondon.Stormzy pleaded guilty to not
OL,10,Fhaving proper control of his vehicle
OL,11,Fand was fined #533 at Croydon
OL,12,FMagistrates' Court.
OL,14,FMagistrate Lynn Keane also ordered him
OL,15,Fto pay #120 costs and a #213 victim
OL,16,Fsurcharge, and handed him three
OL,17,Fpenalty points for his driving licence.
OL,19,FIt is the second time the music
OL,20,Fsuperstar has fallen foul of the law
OL,21,Ffor using his phone at the wheel.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
