CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780585869
OL,3,CStormzy fined for using phone while
OL,4,Cdriving #400,000 Ferrari
OL,6,FIn January 2025, Stormzy was banned
OL,7,Ffrom driving for nine months after an
OL,8,Foff-duty police officer caught him on
OL,9,Fhis phone while driving a Rolls-Royce
OL,10,Fin West Kensington.
OL,12,FHe was handed a #2,010 court bill
OL,13,Fafter pleading guilty and also
OL,14,Fadmitting a second charge of having
OL,15,Foverly tinted windows on his car.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
