OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780585869
OL,3,CStormzy fined for using phone while
OL,4,Cdriving #400,000 Ferrari
OL,6,FAccording to court papers obtained by
OL,7,Fthe Press Association, Stormzy `
OL,8,Fprosecuted under his real name Michael
OL,9,FEbenazer Owuo Junior ` was pulled over
OL,10,Fin his black Ferrari Purosangue at
OL,11,F9.25am on November 10 by Pc Glen
OL,12,FLambert.
OL,14,FThe officer said in a statement that
OL,15,Fhe noticed the driver was "distracted
OL,16,Fand no longer in proper control" of
OL,17,Fthe supercar.
OL,26,@wD@[OUxD@`O]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
