OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780585869
OL,3,CStormzy fined for using phone while
OL,4,Cdriving #400,000 Ferrari
OL,6,F"As I passed the vehicle on the
OL,7,Foffside to filter through traffic I
OL,8,Fnoticed the driver was inputting an
OL,9,Faddress on his maps application on his
OL,10,Fmobile phone," Pc Lambert said.
OL,12,F"From what I had seen of the vehicle's
OL,13,Fmovements I was satisfied that the
OL,14,Fstandard of driving had fallen below
OL,15,Fthat of a driver in full, careful
OL,16,Fcontrol of their vehicle.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@NO]tD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780585869
OL,3,CStormzy fined for using phone while
OL,4,Cdriving #400,000 Ferrari
OL,6,F"I stopped the vehicle and spoke with
OL,7,Fthe driver. The driver confirmed that
OL,8,Fhe had just been setting a route on
OL,9,Fhis maps and that he had only just
OL,10,Fpicked up the device as I passed."
OL,12,FEntering his guilty plea in writing,
OL,13,FStormzy said in mitigation: "I accept
OL,14,FI was putting a location in the map."
OL,16,FThe incident happened a month after he
OL,17,Fhad run out of petrol in the same
OL,18,FFerrari on Putney High Street.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@bO]uD@]OUvD@eO]
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
