OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,403,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F402A1780585869
OL,3,CStormzy fined for using phone while
OL,4,Cdriving #400,000 Ferrari
OL,6,FWhile waiting for assistance, the
OL,7,Frapper staged an impromptu meet-and-
OL,8,Fgreet with fans and posted a video of
OL,9,Fthe incident.
OL,11,FAfter his latest conviction, Stormzy
OL,12,Fwas given a month to settle the total
OL,13,Fcourt bill of #866.
OL,15,FHis prosecution was dealt with by the
OL,16,FSingle Justice Procedure on May 7, in
OL,17,Fa private hearing which he was not
OL,18,Frequired to attend.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
